Class GetTaskResultServlet

All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig
public class GetTaskResultServlet
extends WekaServlet

Get the result of a task (if available). For clients it returns the TaskStatusInfo (which encapsulates the result). So in this case is the same as the GetTaskStatusServlet. For browsers the servlet prints out the result as a string.
